{
  "text": "Indirect immunocytochemistry showed a punctate label pattern on PC3 cell membranes (Fig. 4A) . The labeling pattern was similar to that described in transfected HEK293-related cells (293/FRT cell line) [CITATION_1] . Immunoblots incubated with MC2R antibody that was pre-absorbed with commercially available MC2R polypeptide showed no band (Fig. 4B) . Routine western blot analysis showed higher MC2R protein expression in LNCaP, PC3, DU-145 cells compared with normal non-tumorigenic RWPE2 prostate cells (Fig. 4C) .",
